{
  "stem": "1160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got all excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes, I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, how would you know that I am his daughter?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, well, you look like-- just like him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's the same face.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, if you recognize me, I said, from my father, so where is my father?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How do you know him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he says they were together at one part of-- in the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, well, where is he?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, you came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where is he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he says, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I tell you, if your father would be alive, he would-- he would be here, because he was a man, if he would have been locked in a room where there were no doors and no windows, he would have been able to come out from that room and save himself.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was helping people, his comrade there-- his fellow inmates, I should say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was saying-- talking very nice about him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a few years passes and there is another Yizkor on a high holiday and I'm ready to go out and my mother says, you can stay.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So then I knew that I have no more father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no more hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know what with this feeling, what else comes?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even anger came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why is he not back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Why isn't he with us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So some people used to appear who had been away for some time and that's what kept the-- the belief?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We believed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believed my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She believed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She believed it so strong that he's going to come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBBING] You see, he was very good to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
